---
// src/pages/index.astro
---

<html lang="pt-BR">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <title>G STORM - Gestão de Estética Automotiva</title>
    
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  </head>
  <body class="bg-white text-black font-sans antialiased selection:bg-purple-600 selection:text-white">
    
    <header class="fixed w-full top-0 z-50 bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-md border-b border-gray-100">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 h-20 flex items-center justify-between">
        <div class="text-2xl font-extrabold tracking-tight cursor-default">
          G <span class="text-purple-600">STORM</span>
        </div>
        <nav>
          <a href="/login" class="px-6 py-2.5 bg-black hover:bg-purple-600 text-white font-semibold rounded-full transition-all duration-300 shadow-md hover:shadow-purple-600/30 flex items-center gap-2">
            Acessar Painel
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3"></path></svg>
          </a>
        </nav>
      </div>
    </header>

    <main class="pt-32 pb-16 md:pt-48 md:pb-32 px-6">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-extrabold tracking-tight mb-8 text-black">
          Acelere a gestão da sua <br class="hidden md:block" />
          <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-600 to-black">Estética Automotiva</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-500 mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          O sistema definitivo para estúdios de detalhamento. Controle agendamentos, clientes e faturamento em uma plataforma premium, rápida e focada em resultados.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-4">
          <a href="/login" class="px-8 py-4 bg-purple-600 hover:bg-purple-700 text-white font-bold rounded-xl text-lg transition-colors shadow-lg shadow-purple-600/30">
            Começar Agora
          </a>
          <a href="#recursos" class="px-8 py-4 bg-gray-50 hover:bg-gray-100 text-black font-bold rounded-xl text-lg transition-colors border border-gray-200">
            Conhecer Recursos
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>

    <section id="recursos" class="py-24 bg-black text-white px-6">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">Tudo o que seu estúdio precisa</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-400">Desenvolvido para quem entende de detalhe e perfeição.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <div class="bg-gray-900 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-800 hover:border-purple-500 transition-colors group">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-purple-600/20 text-purple-500 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"></path></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Agenda Inteligente</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400">Organize os horários dos boxes, evite choques de clientes e tenha a previsão exata de entrega.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gray-900 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-800 hover:border-purple-500 transition-colors group">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-purple-600/20 text-purple-500 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Controle Financeiro</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400">Acompanhe faturamentos e tickets médios. Saiba exatamente quanto seu estúdio está lucrando.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gray-900 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-800 hover:border-purple-500 transition-colors group">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-purple-600/20 text-purple-500 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"></path></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Gestão de Clientes</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400">Histórico de serviços por veículo e CRM básico para fidelizar seu público e gerar recorrência.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <footer class="bg-black py-8 border-t border-gray-900 text-center text-gray-500 px-6">
      <p>© 2026 G STORM. Todos os direitos reservados.</p>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>